ns0:foreignObject.html:div: Look carefully at the illustration showing elements of the weather. Identify the different parts and think about what they represent. Use your observations to answer the questions that follow.

ns0:svg.ns0:text: 1. What are the main things you see in this picture related to the weather?
2. Can you point out and name two things in the picture that are related to the sun and its effect on the weather?
3. What does the picture tell you about how the weather might be on the day shown? Is it sunny, rainy, or something else?
4. How do the elements shown in the picture affect the weather where you live? Give an example.
5. If you were to add one more element to the picture to make it more complete in terms of showing different types of weather, what would you add and why?
